{"tid":804288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵又逢水災！沙中線地盤水浸　禍及鑽石山站","createTime":"2018-09-03T02:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T02:55:42.000Z","uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0665a19b915206501adbe2fceb8c744d9a4fed22","tid":804288,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"大雨滂沱下，鑽石山港鐵站近彩虹道出口旁的沙中線地盤今早(7日)約6時半，疑因排水泵故障致水浸，積水從地盤滲出，沿斜路流向港鐵站A2出口，浸濕扶手電梯，並流向大堂，多名職員清理積水及堆放沙包，A2出口封閉約1小時後才解封。<br />\n<br />\n該港鐵站A1出入口近機房位置亦有漏水情況，以致地面濕滑，一度封閉。至於站內秩序正常，未有影響列車服務。港鐵發言人指，事發後車站已即時加派人手到場處理，堆疊沙包防止雨水流入車站及疏導雨水，維修人員亦在場確保車站排水系統暢通。<br />\n<br />\n發言人續稱，為審慎起見，A1及A2出入口一度需要暫時封閉，職員指示乘客用其他出入口進出車站，站內亦加派車站助理協助乘客及維持車站秩序。至約8時，A1出入口局部開放，僅讓乘客進入車站，2個出入口至9時方正式重開。事件期間列車服務則未有受影響，車站運作亦大致暢順。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵因天雨而發生水浸並不鮮見，昨(6日)有網民在社交群組上載一段港鐵滲水的片段，只見雨水不斷從車門間的隙縫噴入車廂，車門下方不斷有雨水湧入，形成小水氹，並流入乘客座位下方。高鐵西九龍站昨亦不敵黃雨考驗，發生嚴重漏水事故，牽涉站內多個樓層，出現「層層滴」慘況，B1售票大堂層、B3內地出入境層及B4月台層多處出現漏水，地面積水如水塘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=b3ad5552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=ebb3fc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=6a96995d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_04p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=5b8eae2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_05p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=daabcb0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_06p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=82b56225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/photo/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_07p.jpg?20180607154428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20180607154428&h=03900702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180607%2Fbkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001.html&d=ndkQznoxMezB%2Fw7L1lA0CGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=cb60241d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180607/bkn-20180607083214000-0607_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"56cd5102a0c14ff32058a0ac9a0b7cf23e3cf3c4","tid":804288,"uid":37546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"0607 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f1c26239b1260c